data.description: Buyers financing fell through! Motivated Sellers! This enchanting home offers a warm and inviting atmosphere that you'll love coming home to. Quaint single story ranch home on a quiet street in a well established neighborhood right in the heart of Columbia! This perfectly located home features~ 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath ranch comes with a HUGE Florida room, a Bonus space, Workshop and Extra Storage room! Relax and unwind in the cozy living room, where you can curl up with a good book or gather with loved ones for laughter-filled movie nights  This All Brick home offers beautiful Original Hard Wood floors and Spacious Bedrooms! For additional questions call listing agent Miles Duncan - 931-797-3277.
